		CHANGES in sfsmisc VERSION 1.0-0  [2007-12-10]

NEW FEATURES

   o	plotDS() is new name for pl.ds() now allows 'ys' to be a smooth
	"fit structure".  That is now easily constructed via

   o	new seqXtend() function for constructing a sequence which includes
	a give set of numbers x.

   o	y <- roundfixS(x) yields integers y[i] with the same sum as x[i].


		CHANGES in sfsmisc VERSION 0.96-01  [2007-11-21]

NEW FEATURES

   o	new function eaxis() for "engineering" / "extended" axis
	drawing, notably for log-axis labeling


		CHANGES in sfsmisc VERSION 0.95-13  [2007-09-13]

NEW FEATURES

   o	new function nearcor() {find nearest correlation matrix};
	almost as donated by Jens Oehlschlaegel.

BUG FIXES

   o	pdf.latex(), pdf.do() : defaults; viewer specifications...


		CHANGES in sfsmisc VERSION 0.95-12  [2007-06-30]
NEW FEATURES

   o	New internal Sys.procinfo() function for cleaner implementation of
   	Sys.cpuinfo() and Sys.meminfo().


		CHANGES in sfsmisc VERSION 0.95-10  [2007-06-25]

